  <brief_title>Evaluation of Safety and Efficacy of 17-Beta Estradiol in Treatment of Atrophic Vaginitis: An Extension Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Safety and Efficacy of 17-Beta Estradiol in Treatment of Estrogen Deficiency-Derived Atrophic Vaginitis</official_title>
